econdary-font pi-secondary-background pi-item-spacing\">Chapter Chronology</caption>\n\t\n\t<tbody>\n\t<tr>\n\t\n\t\t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\">← <a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_35\" title=\"Chapter 35\">Previous</a></td>\n\t\n\t\t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_37\" title=\"Chapter 37\">Next</a> →</td>\n\t\n\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n</section>\n</aside>\n\n</p><p><b>Chapter 36</b> is titled \"After Them!!\".\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Cover_Page\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Cover Page</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Short_Summary\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Short Summary</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Long_Summary\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Long Summary</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quick_Reference\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quick Reference</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Chapter_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chapter Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Characters\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Characters</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Author_Comment\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Author Comment</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Trivia\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Trivia</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#Site_Navigation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Site Navigation</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Cover_Page\">Cover Page</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_36%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D1&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Buggy%27s_Crew_Adventure_Chronicles\" title=\"Buggy&#39;s Crew Adventure Chronicles\">Buggy's Crew Adventure Chronicles</a>, Vol. 2: \"<a href=\"/wiki/Mohji\" title=\"Mohji\">Mohji</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Cabaji\" title=\"Cabaji\">Cabaji</a>\".\n</p><p>Their <a href=\"/wiki/Buggy\" title=\"Buggy\">captain</a> gone and his two strongest lieutenants badly beaten, the <a href=\"/wiki/Buggy_Pirates\" title=\"Buggy Pirates\">Buggy Pirates</a> are unceremoniously chased out of <a href=\"/wiki/Orange_Town\" title=\"Orange Town\">Orange Town</a> by <a href=\"/wiki/Chouchou\" title=\"Chouchou\">Chouchou</a> and a mob of angry citizens.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Short_Summary\">Short Summary</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_36%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D2&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Usopp\" title=\"Usopp\">Usopp</a> is unable to move anymore to protect <a href=\"/wiki/Kaya\" title=\"Kaya\">Kaya</a> but he has not lost his will. <a href=\"/wiki/Roronoa_Zoro\" title=\"Roronoa Zoro\">Zoro</a> finally defeats <a href=\"/wiki/Buchi\" title=\"Buchi\">Buchi</a> and brings Usopp up on his back so they can catch up with Kaya and the children before <a href=\"/wiki/Jango\" title=\"Jango\">Jango</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/Kuro\" title=\"Kuro\">Kuro</a> tries to stop them but finding&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Luffy</a> in his way, they start to fight each other. Meanwhile Jango has found where the escapee were hidden.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Long_Summary\">Long Summary</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_36%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D3&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Piiman\" title=\"Piiman\">Piiman</a> asks the other <a href=\"/wiki/Usopp_Pirates\" title=\"Usopp Pirates\">Usopp Pirates</a> to look back to see if Jango is following them as they escort <a href=\"/wiki/Kaya\" title=\"Kaya\">Kaya</a> through the forest. Just as they think they are safe, Jango's ring comes flying out through the trees in their direction, barely missing them but cutting up every tree they fly through. <a href=\"/wiki/Jango\" title=\"Jango\">Jango</a> tells them he is prepared to destroy the whole forest in order to find them.\n</p><p>The echoes of Jango chasing after the others can be heard back at the coastline. <a href=\"/wiki/Kuro\" title=\"Kuro\">Kuro</a> tells <a href=\"/wiki/Usopp\" title=\"Usopp\">Usopp</a> he has no feelings for Miss Kaya and if she does just happen to survive, he might thank her for being part of his scheme. As Usopp makes a break for it in order to aid Miss Kaya and the others, <a href=\"/wiki/Buchi\" title=\"Buchi\">Buchi</a> makes an attempt to once again get in the way, but <a href=\"/wiki/Roronoa_Zoro\" title=\"Roronoa Zoro\">Zoro</a> once again blocks, this time he wastes no time with him. As Usopp makes another break for it, he falls to the ground too weak to continue on while Kuro laughs at his efforts. Usopp knows he cannot win, but is prepared to fight anyway.\n</p><p>Buchi tosses Zoro aside again. The other <a href=\"/wiki/Black_Cat_Pirates\" title=\"Black Cat Pirates\">Black Cat Pirates</a> mock Usopp and get a boulder thrown at them from Luffy. Zoro loses his temper at Buchi and finally makes the finishing strike against him. With Buchi out of the way, Zoro takes Usopp and heads out after Kaya and the others. Kuro attempts to prevent Zoro and Usopp from leaving, but Luffy sees to it that they are allowed to leave. Unfortunately, Kuro dodges the attack. Kuro then strikes back at Luffy, whom in turn strikes at him. Kuro now concentrates on Luffy only. Kuro asks Luffy why he fights for the village as an outside. Luffy tells him there is someone in the village he won't let die.\n</p><p>In the forest, Zoro's bad sense of direction is hindering his attempt to locate Kaya, even with Usopp's help. Elsewhere in the forest, Kaya is beginning to feel the height of her illness as the running around is bringing on her fever. The Usopp Pirates urge her on, but she asks them to leave which they refuse to. Jango finally catches up with them.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quick_Reference\">Quick Reference</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_36%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D4&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chapter_Notes\">Chapter Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_36%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D5&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Roronoa_Zoro\" title=\"Roronoa Zoro\">Zoro</a> defeats <a href=\"/wiki/Buchi\" title=\"Buchi\">Buchi</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Luffy</a> and Kuro begin their battle.</li>\n<li>Zoro and <a href=\"/wiki/Usopp\" title=\"Usopp\">Usopp</a> begin to search for <a href=\"/wiki/Kaya\" title=\"Kaya\">Kaya</a> and the <a href=\"/wiki/Usopp_Pirates\" title=\"Usopp Pirates\">Usopp Pirates</a>.</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters\">Characters</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_36%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D6&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table class=\"CharTable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/Pirate\" title=\"Pirate\">Pirates</a>\n</th>\n<th>Citizens\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Straw_Hat_Pirates\" title=\"Straw Hat Pirates\">Straw Hat Pirates</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Monkey D. Luffy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Roronoa_Zoro\" title=\"Roronoa Zoro\">Roronoa Zoro</a></li></ul>\n<hr />\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Black_Cat_Pirates\" title=\"Black Cat Pirates\">Black Cat Pirates</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Kuro\" title=\"Kuro\">Kuro</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Jango\" title=\"Jango\">Jango</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Buchi\" title=\"Buchi\">Buchi</a></li></ul>\n<hr />\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Buggy_Pirates\" title=\"Buggy Pirates\">Buggy Pirates</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Mohji\" title=\"Mohji\">Mohji</a> (cover)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Richie\" title=\"Richie\">Richie</a> (cover, K.O)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Cabaji\" title=\"Cabaji\">Cabaji</a> (cover)</li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Syrup_Village\" title=\"Syrup Village\">Syrup Village</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Kaya\" title=\"Kaya\">Kaya</a></li></ul>\n<hr />\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Usopp_Pirates\" title=\"Usopp Pirates\">Usopp Pirates</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Usopp\" title=\"Usopp\">Usopp</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Piiman\" title=\"Piiman\">Piiman</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Ninjin\" title=\"Ninjin\">Ninjin</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Tamanegi\" title=\"Tamanegi\">Tamanegi</a></li></ul>\n<hr />\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Orange_Town\" title=\"Orange Town\">Orange Town</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Boodle\" title=\"Boodle\">Boodle</a> (cover)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Chouchou\" title=\"Chouchou\">Chouchou</a> (cover)</li></ul>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Author_Comment\">Author Comment</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_36%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D7&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><br />\n</p><table class=\"wikitable\" style=\"margin: auto; text-align: center; width:50%\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_WSJ_Author_Comments\" title=\"List of WSJ Author Comments\">Author Comment</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:90%\"><div class=\"tabber wds-tabber\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__wrapper with-bottom-border\"><ul class=\"wds-tabs\"><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab wds-is-current\" data-hash=\"Translation\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Translation</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"Original\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Original</a></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content wds-is-current\"><p><br />\nThank you for sending me all the <i>One Piece</i> cosplay pictures. If I did it I'd be a fabulous Nami ♥ Yikes.</p></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content\"><p><br />\nワンピースのコスプレ写真色々と送ってくれてありがとう。僕がやるならやっぱりナミかしら♡ぎゃあ。</p></div></div>—<a href=\"/wiki/Eiichiro_Oda\" title=\"Eiichiro Oda\">Eiichiro Oda</a></td><td><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Eiichiro_Oda\" title=\"Eiichiro Oda\"><img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/a/ad/Eiichiro_Oda_WSJ_Avatar.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20230801133230\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"Eiichiro Oda WSJ Avatar.png\" data-image-key=\"Eiichiro_Oda_WSJ_Avatar.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"><i>English translation by <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.thegrandline.com/odatocLIVE.htm\">Greg Werner</a>. For comprehensive translation credits, see <a href=\"/wiki/List_of_WSJ_Author_Comments#Translation_Credits\" title=\"List of WSJ Author Comments\">here</a>.</i></td></tr>\n\n</tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\">Trivia</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_36%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D8&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Reportedly, Luffy's threat to the Black Cat Pirates is the only time in the manga he seriously uses the word \"kill\"<span style=\"font-weight: normal\"> (<span class=\"t_nihongo_kanji\" lang=\"ja\">殺す</span><span class=\"t_nihongo_comma\">,</span> <i><span class=\"t_nihongo_romaji\">Korosu</span></i><span class=\"t_nihongo_help\"><sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:Japanese\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Help:Japanese\"><span class=\"t_nihongo_icon\" style=\"color:#00e;font:bold 80% sans-serif;text-decoration:none;padding:0 .1em;\">?</span></a></sup></span>)</span>. In <a href=\"/wiki/SBS_Volume_57#Chapter_555.2C_Page_80\" title=\"SBS Volume 57\">a later SBS</a>, Oda recounts that his grandmother had cautioned him against using the word too freely.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Site_Navigation\">Site Navigation</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_36%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D9&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"toccolours\" style=\"margin:auto; text-align:center; width:80%;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left;\">\n<p><b>← <a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_35\" title=\"Chapter 35\">Previous Chapter</a></b>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:right;\">\n<p><b><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_37\" title=\"Chapter 37\">Next Chapter</a> →</b>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"toccolours\" style=\"margin:auto; font-size:90%; clear:both; text-align:center; width:80%;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th class=\"cs EastBlueSagaColors\" style=\"\" colspan=\"12\"><a href=\"/wiki/Syrup_Village_Arc\" title=\"Syrup Village Arc\">Syrup Village Arc</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"cs EastBlueSagaColors\" style=\"\" colspan=\"12\"><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Syrup_Village_Arc_Chapters\" title=\"Category:Syrup Village Arc Chapters\">Manga Chapters</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_22\" title=\"Chapter 22\">22</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_23\" title=\"Chapter 23\">23</a